snippet.title: Pet Shows trailer
snippet.description:
From the creators of the hugely popular Permia - Duels comes Pet Shows, the pet manager game for all ages!

Create your personal dream team! Cats, dogs, rabbits, rodents and lizards - Pet Shows has more than 300 different animals to collect.

Manage and train your team! See your pets grow from babies to adults, improve their abilities with training and boost them with a variety of awesome accessories.

Download from Windows Phone store:
http://www.windowsphone.com/s?appid=18b5216c-4f43-412a-a90e-6c9a08b6372c
